and Deathcaller's Stonewind:
<br />

<br />
<a target="_new" href="http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/item.aspx?item=68773">http://www.eqdiva.com/eq/items/item.aspx?item=68773</a>
<br />

<br />
(which btw needs to be updated to show that it has a right clicky of War March of the Mastruq on it)
<br />

<br />
Anyway, they both say they are Pri/Sec but I can only equip one or the other along with a weapon - I can't equip both.  Is that intentional?  I would sure love to equip both.  The stats are awesome.
<br />

