				<td colspan="2"><span>Starrsong was my first toon - and is my main - and I have played her since I created her on Oct 19, 2000.  I am one of those old fogeys whos only previous computer game addiction was Tetris.  My memory isn't as good as it should be, and I found this game to be very complicated when I began it.  Though I have learned a lot - I still don't remember every single detail.  I have a RL and my available time is usually spent playing - not trolling these boards - so I am guilty of missing some of the ins and outs that I might have found here.
<br />

<br />
This is the first time, that I can recall, that I had 2 instruments that were both Pri/Sec equipable.  And with such awesome stats, it would have been incredible to use them both at the same time.  
<br />

<br />
I came here - thinking I was asking a simple question.
<br />

