You say you didn't come to the realization that 2 instruments couldn't be equipped together until about level 50.  That seems a bit late to me but not too incredibly so.  But at 50, there is a LOT still to learn about barding.  By the time you are raiding level 73 and level 75 mobs in Elementals and GoD there aren't any basics that you should be lacking.
<br />

<br />
And make no mistake:  knowledge of instruments is a barding basic.
<br />

<br />
