				<td colspan="2"><span>I think it is easiest to remember that way: You can never dual wield an instrument in secondary slot. In primary slot instruments are 1 handed objects, in secondary slot they become 2 handed objects. That takes care of every possibility to equip instruments I think.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />
Consequently you can't equip two instruments as the one in secondary will act as a 2 handed object, not allowing to be put anything in primary slot.
<br />
And don't worry, I'm 20 and my memory starts to scare me already... ;)
<br />
Oh, one more word if I may... I don't think you have to be a certain age to be polite, in my opinion it is more a matter of attitude and respect than one of age.<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
